descriptionHTML:
This Is A JavaScript Code Style Watch Face For Your Android Wear Device.
Perfect For That Geeky Side That Cant Get Enough Of Code.

This Watch Contains:
- Dont Want Date And TIme sepereate? thenchange the face to date and time togeather in settings
- Watch Face Settings
- 12Hr and 24Hr Clock (Changeable With Settings)
- Tap Watch To Reveal Date
- Tap Watch Again to Reveal Battery
- Changeable Output For The Time Screen Functions: I.E: procrastinate.start(); can be changed in settings: to code.start(); ~ (There are a total of 10 different words that can be implemented)
- Changeable Output For The Date Screen Functions: I.E: tomorrow.work(); can be changed in settings: to tomorrow.sleep(); ~ (There are a total of 7 different words that can be implemented)
- Code Based Humour ... ish
- 6 Selectable Themes
- Battery Text Changes Depends On Battery Level.

You Can Find Out More Information & Change Log Here: https://forum.xda-developers.com/android-wear/development/watchface-watchface-js-javascript-t3561859
Change Log Available Here: https://www.reddit.com/r/androidwatchfaces/comments/5vq1rg/watchface_watch_facejs_javascript_styled_watch/
